Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 全世界的少男少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你們也有準時收看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到了JUDATV的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤機關的壞人又欺負我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提一點反對意見就被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們作對的話會被帶去可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有言論自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說這種紙扇也要被禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真是渣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙扇是我的愛與靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩絆他們總是那麼好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看這種節目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDATV播出的時候沒法換頻道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤機關的確很強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有許多ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以全世界的國家都對他們唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許聽信了服從他們就停止戰爭的言論
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道他們什麼時候會出爾反爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們JUDA可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就豁出性命在和加藤機關作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有人因為好友被加藤機關所殺才加入JUDA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是笨手笨腳的外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中成長起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在最前線戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來時 我們已經被他超過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓他獨自出風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家助一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的節目到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤機關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我玩玩吧 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中斷播出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯絆 收工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DECEIVE撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真不帶勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地趕來 太掃興了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 遠藤兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲 快看這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳槽去給兒童電視台做保鏢了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有自己知道自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會向世界證明JUDA的正當性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我們可不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第18話 牢記死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼矢島要這樣對我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏面是鄂霍次克海的島嶼資料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該曾是俄羅斯的核潛艇基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 我也想立刻就去營救城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的JUDA裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在前線作戰的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果傻乎乎的中招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興的是加藤機關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨在說人話!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 這麼聰明的浩一不是浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是矢島的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會加害城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得相信?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在是加藤機關的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被上面命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島不會做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島總是保護著我和浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個加藤機關不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巨大的機器人和矢島的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及打傷降矢的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島在加藤機關成為了那台MACHINA的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一也駕駛同樣的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一突然變強也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒告訴她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我啊 為什麼矢島會那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島是為了理沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一 說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓矢島自己說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 降矢那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨 你還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快去救城崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總司令恩准了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次總算能幹掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為大哥報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種花招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 真崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球體發生領域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干涉開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是設置球體時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 扭曲空司的電磁波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算用它中和我們的護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏這時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨 你去救城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 這裏交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思前顧後不像你的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨還是單純點好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就沒大腦 再考慮也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎起到你大腦的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趕快找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子正身陷危機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDA和御崎町有我們保護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪美就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找矢島…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧 兩根角的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護浩一的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤 久嵩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎繪美…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未抵達這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎和矢島中途繞道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們邊談邊等他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉對你動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤久嵩會來這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 把你交給總司令前有話要問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你喜歡浩一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是俄羅斯的核潛艇基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經被加藤機關接收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都是我們的好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於城崎繪美的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你最瞭解矢島英明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對矢島做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時沒有因子的APARESHION
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即找到了新的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有幸被選中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是回收了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APARESHION的D-SOIL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有LINEBARREL那樣卓越的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全復活需要花費時日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是矢島干的那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試問早瀨浩一同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被LINEBARREL復活後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前判若兩人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你喜歡浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才留在他身邊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡還纏著他?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純把他作為LINEBARREL的因子利用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙騙浩一讓他上戰場賣命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總在浩一身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排斥理沙子讓她傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不喜歡浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還穿上這種衣服給她們看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前勸你來我這邊時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以矢島的事為理由拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有這個問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想邀請我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此一時彼一時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該明白了更多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的力量面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界放棄了抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇虛假的和平 沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中沒有對未來的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只盼望維持現狀閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫ELVIS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉魔盒底留下的「盲目的希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不搞什麼征服世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平還會繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前電影裏曾說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「波魯及亞家族30年的暴政
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出米開朗基羅和達芬奇的文藝復興」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但瑞典500年的和平與民主又孕育出了什麼呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「木偶鍾而已」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出想像需要的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是壓迫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盼望壓迫中解脫會催生想像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最適合讓人發揮想像的壓迫是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存者與死者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們明確劃分開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將成為最大的壓迫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的生命是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能稱之為人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去想像力為活著而活著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不過是服從程序的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與MACHINA無異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要做的是成為「人類」這台MACHINA的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為所有這一切的「殺人因子」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想像力的MACHINA們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被我們這些因子淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有掙扎著想活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能察覺到作為人活下去的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是加藤機關的征服世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想把握住真正的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來加藤機關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但希望你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡他的話就離開浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在浩一身邊會有女孩傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就想著浩一 為他努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純一心一意的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再折磨她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡理沙子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初怨恨自己的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會把這樣的人選作因子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在是為了戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護世界的使命?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法得出答案的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能親自動手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該繼續留在浩一身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護罩被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BARRET ARM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想前進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縮小護罩範圍2公里重新展開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算躲在護罩裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹掉那個大塊頭就沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裏頂住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到浩一回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我們重新展開護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠自己的力量誓死保衛這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一和我都是正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸給繪美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一真是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就喊著要當正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是被人欺負 所以我們都保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的早瀨有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保護你們不是理所應當的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子 暫時留在這裏看著早瀨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的人類是無力的MACHINA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必豁出性命保護那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也許不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢怒不敢言的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為微不足道的夢想忍辱負重的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有抗爭的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是城崎帶給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非自己爭取到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的正義也許是不值一提的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是想成為真正的正義使者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記茱迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘記石神大叔的誠懇請求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多弱小的人就像我以前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有信任我支持我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遍佈整個世界的"MACHINA"們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把城崎繪美帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按您的指示 收容在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經沒有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨 帶著她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走地下通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次戰場上見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三丁目的護罩消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天津大道到阪井重新展開護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御崎的特自部隊後退至站前區域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好的不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明早瀨浩一確實超越了想像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃能縮短兩個步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了浩一他們才接受了那種命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他們倆人回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有任何改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對你更好不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨浩一和城崎繪美如果進展順利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我並沒有成為你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不利己 專門利人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人想起你 你也只為世界而活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後也為它而死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島說的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨對理沙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎身上的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢島的吧
